"Inyandiko Nka iyi Na: ku i Verisiyo Bya &kspread; ku Ibiro . Gukata Hasi ku "
"Bya i ya:  , Ryari: Itangira Tangira &vendorShortName; Kuri Koresha "
"&kspread; Gushyiraho i Mburabuzi Amahitamo in Byose Amapaji Bya i &kspread; "
"Iboneza Ikiganiro ( ku <menuchoice> <guimenu> </guimenu> <guimenuitem> ... </"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ) ya:  <guilabel> Ubwoko </guilabel> in i "
"<guisubmenu> </guisubmenu> Ipaji: , Gushyiraho Kuri <guimenuitem> </"
