#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:345
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Sums"
msgstr "Byoroheje"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:346
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the first character in a cell is an equals sign (<keycap>=</keycap>) "
"&sheets; will take the cell contents to be a formula which is to be "
"calculated. The result of the calculation will be displayed in the cell "
"rather than the formula itself. For example, enter <userinput>=2+3</"
"userinput> into a cell and it should display <emphasis>5</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"i Itangira Inyuguti: in A Akazu ni Shyiraho Umukono ( <keycap> = </keycap> ) "
"&kspread; i Akazu Ibigize Kuri A Inzira ni Kuri . Igisubizo Bya i Imibare  "
"in i Akazu i Inzira . Urugero: , Injiza <userinput> = 2 + 3 </userinput> A "
"Akazu na Kugaragaza: <emphasis> 5 </emphasis> . "

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:351
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More usefully, a formula can contain references to other cells, so that "
"<userinput>=B4+A3</userinput> will calculate the sum of the values in cells "
"B4 and A3, and this calculation will be updated whenever cells B4 or A3 are "
"changed."
msgstr ""
", A Inzira Indango Kuri Ikindi Utudirishya , <userinput> = + </userinput> "
"Kubara i Igiteranyo Bya i Uduciro in Utudirishya na , na iyi Imibare  "
"Utudirishya Cyangwa Byahinduwe . "

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:355
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as addition, a formula can make use of the <keycap>-</keycap> symbol "
"for subtraction, <keycap>*</keycap> for multiplication, and <keycap> /</"
"keycap> to perform division. The round bracket symbols <keycap>(</keycap> "
"and <keycap>)</keycap> can also be used as in normal algebra, so you could "
"enter more complex formulae such as <userinput>=((B10 + C3) *5 - F11) / 2 </"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nka Guteranya + , A Inzira Ubwoko Koresha Bya i <keycap> - </keycap> "
"IKIMENYETSO ya:  Gukuramo , <keycap> * </keycap> ya:  Gukuba (*) , na "
"<keycap> /</keycap> Kuri . IBURUNGUSHURA Ibimenyetso <keycap> ( </keycap> na "
"<keycap> ) </keycap> Byakoreshejwe Nka in Bisanzwe , Injiza Birenzeho "
"ITSINDA RY'IMIBARE C Nka <userinput> = ( ( + ) * 5 - ) /2 </userinput> . "

#. Tag: para
